test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (9 == 3)

 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x72052a490940> = [[537, 1, 537, 1, 537], [1, 537, 1, 537], [537, 1, 537], [1, 537], [537], [1, 537, 1, 537, 1, 537], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 83156680161 == 537
 +  where 83156680161 = <built-in function prod>([3, 179, 537, 1, 3, 179, ...])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
